    <title lang="it">Serse' di Haendel all'Opera di Rouen</title>
    <desc lang="it">Serse Opera in three acts by Georg Friedrich Handel (1685 - 1759) Libretto by Nicolo Minato and Silvio Stampiglia First performnce in London, King's Theatre, 15 April 1738 Opéra de Rouen Normandie Orchestra, David Bates (Musical direction, harpsichord) Clarac &amp; Deloeuil &gt; The Lab (Stage Direction, sets, costumes) Christophe Pitoiset (Set design collaboration), Lodie Kardouss (Artistic collaboration), Rick Martin (Lights), Julien Roques and Benjamin Juhel (Video), Julien Roques (Graphic design), Luc Bourrousse (Dramaturgy) Jake Arditti (Serse) Jakub Józef Orlinski (Arsamene) Cecilia Molinari (Amastre) Mari Eriksmoen (Romilda) Sophie Junker (Atalanta) Luigi de Donato (Ariodate) Elviro Riccardo (Novaro) Rouen, Théâtre des Arts, March 14, 2023.</desc>
    <date>2023</date>
    <category lang="it">opera</category>
    <icon src="https://ptv-prod.wpcdn.pl/media/akpa4984463.jpg" />
  </programme>
