    <title lang="it">Le nozze di Figaro by Mozart at the Salzburg Festival</title>
    <desc lang="it">Le nozze di Figaro 'Opera buffa' in four acts by Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart (1756 - 1791) Libretto by Lorenzo Da Ponte based on 'La folle journée, ou le Mariage de Figaro' by Pierre-Augustin Caron de Beaumarchais First performance in Vienna, Burgtheater, 1 May 1786 Vienna Philharmonic Orchestra, Raphaël Pichon (Conductor) Martin Kusej (Stage director) Raimund Orfeo Voigt (Set designer), Alan Hranitelj (Costume designer), Friedrich Rom (Lighting designer) Krzysztof Bączyk (Figaro) Sabine Devieilhe (Susanna) Andre Schuen (Il Conte di Almaviva) Adriana González (La Contessa di Almaviva) Léa Desandre (Cherubino) Peter Kálmán (Bartolo) Kristina Hammarström (Marcellina) Manuel Günther (Basilio) Serafina Starke (Barbarina) Rafał Pawnuk (Antonio) Andrew Morstein (Don Curzio) Salzburg Festival, 27 July 2023.</desc>
